180
00:14:13,070 --> 00:14:14,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa?</font>

181
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak pernah berpikir...</font>

182
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:22,560
