311
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Betapa memalukan!</font>

312
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:46,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia seharusnya tidak menginginkan
wanita pada saat seperti ini!</font>

313
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengar, aku pergelangan kakiku sakit.</font>

314
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:57,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Jin Hee. Kau terlihat sedih hari ini.</font>

315
00:25:59,990 --> 00:26:01,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?</font>

316
00:26:01,330 --> 00:26:02,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menangkapku.</font>

317
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:04,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bersedih.</font>

318
00:26:04,370 --> 00:26:07,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau membiarkan dirimu bersedih,
