<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan?</font>

344
00:27:29,090 --> 00:27:30,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menyukainya?</font>

345
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

346
00:27:32,300 --> 00:27:33,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

347
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:39,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana aku memanggilmu setelah kau menikah?</font>

348
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:41,520
