602
00:45:23,840 --> 00:45:25,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, itu benar.</font>

603
00:45:25,520 --> 00:45:26,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengambilnya.</font>

604
00:45:26,740 --> 00:45:28,670
