694
00:52:44,280 --> 00:52:46,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku membuat keputusan yang sangat sulit bagi mereka!</font>

695
00:52:46,600 --> 00:52:47,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka harus bersyukur!</font>

696
00:52:50,460 --> 00:52:53,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa wanita begitu egois?</font>

